baka"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-92f","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23916,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/10\/26\/fudayl-forgive-defeat-shaytan\/","url_meta":{"origin":34735,"position":0},"title":"Fudayl on Mercy: Whoever forgives others has defeated Satan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 26, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Razin reported: A man came to Al-Fudayl ibn Bazwan, may Allah have mercy on him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, a man has slandered you!\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cVerily, I will infuriate the one who commanded him! May Allah forgive me and forgive him.\u201d It was said, \u201cWho has commanded him?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33816,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/25\/fudayl-always-recommend-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":34735,"position":1},"title":"Fudayl on Forgiveness: Always recommend mercy and forbearance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdu Samad reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf a man comes to you complaining about another man, then say: O brother, forgive him, as forgiveness is closer to righteousness. If he says my heart cannot tolerate forgiveness, but rather retaliation as Allah Almighty has\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32459,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/fudayl-tawhid-benefit-harm\/","url_meta":{"origin":34735,"position":2},"title":"Fudayl on Tawhid: Only Allah can truly bring benefit, cause harm","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sari ibn al-Mughallis reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever fears Allah, no one can harm him. Whoever fears another besides Allah, no one can benefit him.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 936 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u063a\u064e\u0644\u0651\u0650\u0633\u0650 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0636\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0636 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0627\u0641\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/04\/fudayl-ignorant-sultan\/","url_meta":{"origin":34735,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Sultan: Ignorant rulers ascend when believers disobey Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn al-Ash\u2019ath reported: Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty revealed to some of His Prophets: When those who know Me disobey Me, I will make them be ruled by those who do not know Me.\u201d Source: al-'Uqu\u0304ba\u0304t li-Ibn Abi\u0304 Dunya\u0304 33 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25240,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/04\/fudayl-virtue-sabr-humility\/","url_meta":{"origin":34735,"position":4},"title":"Fudayl on Virtue: What is humility? What is patience?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibrahim ibn al-Ash\u2019at reported: I asked Al-Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cWhat is humility?\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cIt is to humble yourself for the truth, to act in accordance with it, and to accept it even if you hear it from a child.\u201d I asked, \u201cWhat is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33671,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/fudayl-many-scholars-few-wise\/","url_meta":{"origin":34735,"position":5},"title":"Fudayl on Hikmah: Many scholars but few who have wisdom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: A man said to Al-Fudayl, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cThe scholars are many.\u201d Al-Fudayl said, \u201cBut those with wisdom are few.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 8\/92 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u